OL,3,CChildren given digital devices for
OL,4,Ctantrums 'fail to learn emotion
OL,5,Cregulation'
OL,7,FSimply handing a child a mobile phone
OL,8,For tablet when they throw a tantrum
OL,9,Fmay be damaging their ability to
OL,10,Fmanage their emotions, new research
OL,11,Fsuggests.
OL,13,FAccording to the study, if parents
OL,14,Fregularly use digital devices to calm
OL,15,Ftheir children, that child could have
OL,16,Fissues with emotion regulation ` which
OL,17,Fcould lead to anger management
OL,18,Fproblems in later life.
