OL,3,CChildren given digital devices for
OL,4,Ctantrums 'fail to learn emotion
OL,5,Cregulation'
OL,7,FChildren learn a lot about self-
OL,8,Fregulation ` affective, mental, and
OL,9,Fbehavioural responses to certain
OL,10,Fsituations ` during their first few
OL,11,Fyears of life, and this is mainly done
OL,12,Fthrough their relationship with their
OL,13,Fparents, researchers say.
OL,15,FIn recent years, it has become more
OL,16,Fcommon to give children digital
OL,17,Fdevices to control their responses to
OL,18,Femotions, especially if they are
OL,19,Fnegative.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
