OL,3,CChildren given digital devices for
OL,4,Ctantrums 'fail to learn emotion
OL,5,Cregulation'
OL,7,FBut the researchers suggest that if
OL,8,Fpeople knew digital devices were not
OL,9,Fappropriate for dealing with tantrums,
OL,10,Fthe mental health and wellbeing of
OL,11,Fchildren would benefit.
OL,13,FDr Veronika Konok, the study's first
OL,14,Fauthor and a researcher at Eotvos
OL,15,FLorand University in Hungary, said:
OL,16,F"Tantrums cannot be cured by digital
OL,17,Fdevices.
OL,19,F"Children have to learn how to manage
OL,20,Ftheir negative emotions for themselves.
