OL,3,CChildren given digital devices for
OL,4,Ctantrums 'fail to learn emotion
OL,5,Cregulation'
OL,7,F"They need the help of their parents
OL,8,Fduring this learning process, not the
OL,9,Fhelp of a digital device."
OL,11,FShe added: "Here we show that if
OL,12,Fparents regularly offer a digital
OL,13,Fdevice to their child to calm them or
OL,14,Fto stop a tantrum, the child won't
OL,15,Flearn to regulate their emotions.
OL,17,F"This leads to more severe emotion-
OL,18,Fregulation problems, specifically,
OL,19,Fanger management problems, later in
OL,20,Flife."
