OL,7,FSenior author, Professor Caroline
OL,8,FFitzpatrick, a researcher at the
OL,9,FUniversite de Sherbrooke, Canada,
OL,10,Fadded: "We frequently see that parents
OL,11,Fuse tablets or smart phones to divert
OL,12,Fthe child's attention when the child
OL,13,Fis upset.
OL,15,F"Children are fascinated by digital
OL,16,Fcontent, so this is an easy way to
OL,17,Fstop tantrums and it is very effective
OL,18,Fin the short term."
