OL,7,FShe continued: "If people's awareness
OL,8,Fabout digital devices being
OL,9,Finappropriate tools for curing
OL,10,Ftantrums increases, children's mental
OL,11,Fhealth and wellbeing will profit."
OL,13,FHowever, the researchers suspected
OL,14,Fthat over the long term this strategy
OL,15,Fmay not be very beneficial.
OL,17,FIn 2020, they conducted an assessment
OL,18,Fand a followed-up one year later.
