OL,4,Ctantrums 'fail to learn emotion
OL,5,Cregulation'
OL,7,FMore than 300 parents of children aged
OL,8,Fbetween two- and five-years-old
OL,9,Fcompleted a questionnaire which
OL,10,Fassessed child and parent media use.
OL,12,FAccording to the findings, when
OL,13,Fparents used digital emotion
OL,14,Fregulation more often, children showed
OL,15,Fpoorer anger and frustration
OL,16,Fmanagement skills a year later.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
