OL,5,Cregulation'
OL,7,FChildren who were given devices more
OL,8,Foften as they experienced negative
OL,9,Femotions also showed less ability to
OL,10,Fchoose a deliberate response over an
OL,11,Fautomatic one.
OL,13,FThe study, published in Frontiers in
OL,14,FChild and Adolescent Psychiatry, also
OL,15,Ffound that poorer anger management
OL,16,Fskills at the beginning meant children
OL,17,Fwere given digital devices more often
OL,18,Fas a management tool.
