OL,3,CChildren given digital devices for
OL,4,Ctantrums 'fail to learn emotion
OL,5,Cregulation'
OL,7,F"It's not surprising that parents more
OL,8,Ffrequently apply digital emotion
OL,9,Fregulation if their child has emotion
OL,10,Fregulation problems, but our results
OL,11,Fhighlight that this strategy can lead
OL,12,Fto the escalation of a pre-existing
OL,13,Fissue," Dr Konok said.
OL,15,FThe researchers suggest that health
OL,16,Fexperts could provide information on
OL,17,Fhow parents can help their children
OL,18,Fmanage their emotions without giving
OL,19,Fthem tablets or smart phones.
